<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 4 (Jude) - End</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ジュード</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Jude</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ミラ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Milla</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>シュヴァルツはどこに向かったんだろう？
人間を滅ぼす為の力
とか言ってたけど……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Where could Schwartz be heading off to?
She was talking about some power that
could destroy humanity...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>精霊達が教えてくれた。
あいつが向かった先は
エターナルソードが眠る遺跡だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Spirits have told me. She headed
for the ruins where the Eternal Sword rests.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エターナルソード！？
伝説の聖剣が、実在するっていうの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Eternal Sword?! You mean to say
that the legendary holy sword is real?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……ああ。
あいつは……その力で……うっ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...That's right.
She... That power... Ugh!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ミラ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Milla!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>はぁ、はぁ、はぁ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Haa... Haa... Haa...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ひどい。　やっぱり傷口が開いて……。
こんなのとても戦える身体じゃないよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Not good.
Your wound opened, just like I thought it did...
There's no way you can fight like this.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>やっぱりシュヴァルツは
僕が一人でなんとかするべきなんじゃ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Just like I expected, I'll have to do something
about Schwartz on my own somehow...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いいや。
君一人ではシュヴァルツには勝てない。
わかっているのだろう？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No. You won't win against Schwartz on your own.
You're aware of that, aren't you?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>でも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>問題ない。
あいつのもとにエターナルソードがあるなら
一つだけ方法がある……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This isn't a problem. If she has the Eternal Sword,
there's only one thing that can be done...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
